<plot>The streets of LA provide the setting for a lesson in a different kind of cop justice. Detective John Maggette, the leader of a gang of corrupt cops, has been pushed too far. Maggette [Dan Ryder] exploits his control over a prostitute [Nicole Ghastin] to help him re-educate a rogue cop [Nick Rish] bent on making his own deals. But Maggette has a hidden agenda for all. Unwittingly stuck in the middle, the prostitute works her way down the street and down an alley deep into the underbelly of a very dark future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?055852</url></doc>
